          "tz": 60
        },
        "subject": "LU-4643 tests: disable sanity-hsm/test_60 due to failures",
        "message": "LU-4643 tests: disable sanity-hsm/test_60 due to failures\n\nsanity-hsm/test_60 causes numerous auto-test failures.\nTo allow its debugging, it will be disabled in sanity-hsm itself.\nSuspected problems already are 1) a mismatch in the way the CT\nreports progress and how the CDT interpret/report it in the log,\n2) a too short grace_period request causing request to disappear\nfrom the log, 3) a wrong 5242880 size to be checked.\n\nSigned-off-by: Bruno Faccini <bruno.faccini@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I01c70c643af87f63eefc0e3cf4f03a77f7ca8a14\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
